{"tid":598280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何文田女子攀欄河墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-19T11:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T11:36:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"130faa5f4e25d3bde6168e6f61ae2a3f2a44d314","tid":598280,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180319/large/1521453221_4e67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180319%2Flarge%2F1521453221_4e67.jpg&h=6e7b43ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老婦從高處墮下，當場死亡。（姜偉康攝）<br />\n<br />\n下午4時許，一名老婦攜同長梯，在何文田愛民邨昭民樓的高層走廊徘徊，之後爬梯攀過欄河，一躍而下，當場重傷不治。警方到場調查，正調查老婦身份及其墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180319/57968267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F57968267&d=GM7QSPNUochv5gqeLjDBhdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fda52bff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F57968267&h=11f6eb9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180319/57968267</a>"},{"pid":"f2272f3462f3d02fcf9731733462e4de66c7f297","tid":598280,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f3dce08f25eb1bdd756f6f8362baac545ac55a","tid":598280,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e59eaea620c